params.priceFeeds: should all have the same denomination (I.E ETH/USD and BTC/USD), index 0 is ETH
params.tokens: should contain 1 less index than priceFeeds due to ETH balance call

returns.nav: returns the NAV relative to the denominated asset and total baseToken supply
